FIND AND LOCATE 

to locate a file we use locate this requires updatedb -- sudo updatedb locate -- 
	locate filename -- this quickly finds the location of the file
we also use find to locate the files 
	find /path/ -options

		-name  file.txt
		-type f (_f for file d for directory)
		-size +10M 
		-perm 777 
		-user username
		-group groupname 

		
